  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mata's Demise</strong> offers players a single-player, first-person adventure-stealth experience. Navigate the eerie office of <strong>Mata Corporation</strong> as you attempt to escape, with the only way out being up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d7831722c0f698b35a30e6b4a587282d.poster.avif?t=1741051449\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d7831722c0f698b35a30e6b4a587282d.webm?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d7831722c0f698b35a30e6b4a587282d.mp4?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, the office is haunted by vengeful spirits, making every step a careful challenge. Their presence is ever-looming. Do not let them hear you; even worse, do not let them see you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d73c04b18306fdd6d723211eac1284fd.poster.avif?t=1741051449\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d73c04b18306fdd6d723211eac1284fd.webm?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d73c04b18306fdd6d723211eac1284fd.mp4?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The key to your survival lies in mastering stealth and strategy. Mata's Demise incorporates dynamic physics that you can use to your advantage, allowing you to outsmart the spirits and navigate the office more effectively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/fbe2757cebcd1d4805b9b1179ffaa10c.poster.avif?t=1741051449\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/fbe2757cebcd1d4805b9b1179ffaa10c.webm?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/fbe2757cebcd1d4805b9b1179ffaa10c.mp4?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mata's Demise</strong> offers players a single-player, first-person adventure-stealth experience. Navigate the eerie office of <strong>Mata Corporation</strong> as you attempt to escape, with the only way out being up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d7831722c0f698b35a30e6b4a587282d.poster.avif?t=1741051449\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d7831722c0f698b35a30e6b4a587282d.webm?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d7831722c0f698b35a30e6b4a587282d.mp4?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, the office is haunted by vengeful spirits, making every step a careful challenge. Their presence is ever-looming. Do not let them hear you; even worse, do not let them see you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d73c04b18306fdd6d723211eac1284fd.poster.avif?t=1741051449\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d73c04b18306fdd6d723211eac1284fd.webm?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/d73c04b18306fdd6d723211eac1284fd.mp4?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The key to your survival lies in mastering stealth and strategy. Mata's Demise incorporates dynamic physics that you can use to your advantage, allowing you to outsmart the spirits and navigate the office more effectively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/fbe2757cebcd1d4805b9b1179ffaa10c.poster.avif?t=1741051449\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/fbe2757cebcd1d4805b9b1179ffaa10c.webm?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475950/extras/fbe2757cebcd1d4805b9b1179ffaa10c.mp4?t=1741051449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
